<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=1000px, initial-scale=1">
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Portfolio</h2>
    <hr />
    <div class="container">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

            <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
            <div class="carousel-inner">

                <div class="item active">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_docked2.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Docked</h4>
                        <p>
                            Train your manual skills and your thinking at the same time. Rotate and change the color of dots to connect at least 3 of them together. You will love the graphicaly minimal and simple idea of the whole game, starting at the menu finishing on the colorful gameplay.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XRnDOpfYSW8" target="_blank" title="YouTube">
                                <i class="icon-youtube-play"></i>
                                YouTube
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.docked" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/docked/id1167995848?l=pl&ls=1&mt=8" target="_blank" title="AppStore">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_poog.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Poog</h4>
                        <p>
                            You’re building bases for the jumping ball. You never know where the ball will go, but the least bases you’ll slide on the screen the better score you get. It’s simple but not easy so you’ll need to train a lot. In the gameplay you’ll find coins on your way. Collect them and buy yourself some awesome skins.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.slidem" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/poog/id1167045602?l=pl&ls=1&mt=8" target="_blank" title="AppStore">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_funnybunny.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Funny Bunny!</h4>
                        <p>
                            It's minimal, it's simple, it's sweet and so much fun! For a second imagine you're a rabbit in a crazy enviroment trying to collect as many carrots as possible. Try not to get addicted reaching a bigger distance every time you play. Run merrily as far as you can, but watch out for the angry eaters and pointy spikes.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nub2IHz734Q" target="_blank" title="YouTube">
                                <i class="icon-youtube-play"></i>
                                YouTube
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.funny_bunny" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/funny-bunny/id1213351997?l=pl&ls=1&mt=8" target="_blank" title="AppStore">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_tramini2.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Tramini</h4>
                        <p>
                            In development. Coming soon
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="#" title="Google Play (Coming soon)">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play (Coming soon)
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" title="AppStore (Coming soon)">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store (Coming soon)
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_alone.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Not Alone In Space?</h4>
                        <p>
                            You’re a space creature that lost it’s way in the universe. The way home is very long and dangerous. Try to get as high as possible avoiding many different obstacles on the way. Be clever and fast and you’ll gain the best score. On the way you can collect white stars thanks to which you can buy and play different characters.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WcrTbg8jllI" target="_blank" title="YouTube">
                                <i class="icon-youtube-play"></i>
                                YouTube
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.aloneinspace" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" title="AppStore (Coming soon)">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store (Coming soon)
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_rockair.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Rockair</h4>
                        <p>
                            You get to fly many different rockets in the lands of pastel colors and funny clouds. The goal is to fly though mint hoops - collect as many as you can and get the best score. Watch out, you cannot go back and don’t hit the ground, because you’ll explode.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.rockair2" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/rockair/id1212369899?l=pl&ls=1&mt=8" target="_blank" title="AppStore">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="/Content/Images/portfolio_lumbjump.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h4>Lumb Jump</h4>
                        <p>
                            How quick are you? Check if you are quick enough for Lumb Jump! Bounce off from logs as game gets faster, but be swift. Hitting them with your head will hurt. Collect coins to unlock awesome, funny or weird and even manly skins for your character.
                            <hr class="customhr" />
                            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codeaddict.LumpJump" target="_blank" title="Google Play">
                                <i class="icon-googleplay"></i>
                                Google Play
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/lumb-jump/id1191271602?l=pl&ls=1&mt=8" target="_blank" title="AppStore">
                                <i class="icon-appstore"></i>
                                App Store
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Item -->

            </div><!-- End Carousel Inner -->
            <ul class="list-group col-sm-4">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="list-group-item active"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/docked.png" style="width: 45px;">  Docked</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/poog.png" style="width: 45px;">  Poog</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/funnybunny.png" style="width: 45px;">  Funny Bunny!</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/tramini.png" style="width: 45px;">  Tramini</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="4" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/alone.png" style="width: 45px;">  Not Alone In Space?</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="5" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/rockair.png" style="width: 45px;">  Rockair</h4></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="6" class="list-group-item"><h4><img class="roundedimg" src="/Content/Images/Icons/lumbjump.jpg" style="width: 45px;">  Lumb Jump</h4></li>
            </ul>
            <!-- Controls -->
            <div class="carousel-controls">
                <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
                </a>
                <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div><!-- End Carousel -->
    </div>

    <h2>About me</h2>
    <hr />
    <div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
            <p>
                I'm a Unity Developer passionate about games. My passion made me change my carreer from beeing a lawyer to creating video games.
                <br />
                <br />
                At work my main focus is Android and iOS mobile games development with Unity3D game engine. But it's only a tool which serves as a way for bringing my ideas to "life".
                <br />
                <br />
                Currently I'am student of Computer Science at Collegium Da Vinci in Poznań, from which I will graduate with engineering degree in February 2019.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3" style="float: right; margin-right: 100px">
            <script src="//platform.linkedin.com/in.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
            <script type="IN/MemberProfile" data-id="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kaslowinski" data-format="inline" data-related="false">
            </script>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
